title: Johnny Saturn Unlimited (01 - 03) (ongoing) (- Nem -)
description: What does a Brazilian businessman, an old Nazi cybernetics scientist, a pretty-boy detective and a high flying superhero have in common? One man -- Johnny Saturn. This first issue in this award winning series sends the reader into a twisting and turning labyrinth of mystery. It doesn't begin where you think it should, and the ending just leaves you stunned and in awe.
